{"tid":2074701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律政司又再一次俾毅進狗跣 跣到個官審完即日判被告無罪","createTime":"2020-06-22T09:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T17:49:34.000Z","uid":321059,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c82873d3189f394236f433fe2d4e81ddbc0a86cf","tid":2074701,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:58:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200622&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=61084045\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200622%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D61084045&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=b56a62f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200622%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D61084045&h=6e3e0631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200622&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=61084045</a><br />\n<br />\n網民去年11月連日發起三罷及堵路，有地盤判頭晚上在銅鑼灣被警方搜出身藏鎅刀、刀片、石屎釘、石屎鑿及思疑毒品的粉末等物品。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">判頭被拘控，控方早前化驗涉案粉末後，證實並非毒品，撤銷藏毒罪</span></span>；至於管有適合作非法用途的工具罪的案件，今日開審。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被告在盤問下亦透露，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被捕後曾在警署內向警員出示旺角五金舖購物單據，惟警員沒有記錄相關事項，謂「唔需要寫」。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n林官在被告作供後<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">即時作出裁決</span></span>，指本案沒有直接證據證明被告藏有涉案工具作非法用途。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n控方反對辯方的申請，指案發時為社會事件較激烈的時期，而被告攜帶的物品和衣著與「非法人士」相類似。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">控方亦稱，警方一直沒有見過被告到五金舖購物的單據</span></span>，至今天才首次看見。林官最終批准辯方取回訟費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">律政司班高材生律師<br />\n被班狗跣到9告手足之後又撤控<br />\n再俾個官秒速判罪名不成立<br />\n真係顏面何存</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f1b5760a2574ba6f80fab099a125196cbed6d8","tid":2074701,"uid":48130,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:00:43.000Z","msg":"總知班狗咁忠心，肯定係可靠證人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f2580437a621a67a4aedfb501be887cdde5507","tid":2074701,"uid":127929,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:08:35.000Z","msg":"咁可以告返啲狗未"},{"pid":"272103086dea5d20f6c0a0c89dcf9c87641171bd","tid":2074701,"uid":195877,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:09:19.000Z","msg":"DOJ嗰班Prosecution外判嚟咋,鬼係高材生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe3bcb92da2858e4998a56d8649d4745404da4e","tid":2074701,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:10:25.000Z","msg":"阿蛇做野唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12f1769dd64361f31dadbb0a47f9ee0cb50cf50","tid":2074701,"uid":26770,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:11:07.000Z","msg":"其實律政司刑事檢控科班賤種根本無人手<br />\n<br />\n呢d老屈案係班外判狗想討好刑事檢控專員豬狗不如梁卓然<br />\n得到梁書記欣賞幾年升到主任mag仔"},{"pid":"e089977617fe51e4c94fa1ff72762881d7ea11a9","tid":2074701,"uid":150842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:11:19.000Z","msg":"咁人地鳩告冇損失糧照出波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5711429ebba15d0275b44960770497df8b4533d1","tid":2074701,"uid":18596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:11:50.000Z","msg":"瞓左冇睇，律政司唔係under警察？<br />\n叫佢做就做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0dfeda13c1c211f4f430035a9328555ed4ffbe2","tid":2074701,"uid":144811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:12:46.000Z","msg":"科學驗證，冇－隻黑狗popo係誠實可信證人<br />\n係冇一隻！<br />\n完<br />\n法官大人"},{"pid":"fde45248d8d4486b1218095749a41d96785099c2","tid":2074701,"uid":2